# Environment Variables — Enervia

This project is a **static site** and requires no environment variables to run locally.
The following are placeholder variables reserved for future API integration.

Copy this file to `.env` (which is gitignored) if you need to override defaults:

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

---

# Application
VITE_APP_NAME=Enervia
VITE_APP_VERSION=1.0.0
VITE_APP_TAGLINE="Smarter Energy. Greener Living."

# Future API Integration (not currently used)
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.enervia.io/v1
# VITE_SENSOR_WS_URL=wss://live.enervia.io/sensors
# VITE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
